        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Zion Highways, Our heart’s longing, Though pass through Baca valley yet not cease,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All loss count we, Refuse, rubbish; Care for God’s interests, vision ever heed."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "My Lord shall be no more delayed, Be overcomers, pave the way for Him!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Conquering all foes, reigning with Him, How splendid, beauteous, Zion the High Peak!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
